Package: carobiner
Type: Package
Title: Standardizing agricultural research data 
Description: A collection functions to support the "Carob" project to standardize and aggregate open agricultural research data trough reproducible workflows. See https://carob-data.org and https://github.com/carob-data/carob for details.
Version: 0.7-2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: readxl, writexl, httr, data.table, jsonlite, xml2, rappdirs, yuri (>= 0.2-5), vocal (>= 0.3-5)
Remotes: github::carob-data/yuri, github::controvoc/vocal
Suggests: terra, revtools, stringr, rmarkdown, kableExtra, summarytools
